<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="alarm-vt">alarm <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /alarm/    美 /alarm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-worry">1.★ <strong>使惊恐；使担忧(worry)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The news that the enemies were near alarmed everybody.
敌军迫近的消息使大家感到恐慌。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>alarmed /ə'lɑːrmd/ adj <br />
alarming /ə'lɑːrmɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>